CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 26, 1961, pg. A13 reads: "Leaving Church - Mr. and Mrs. William Henry Lewis smile for the photographer as they leave St. Richard Roman Catholic Church, following their recent wedding. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom William Henry Lewis wearing light colored dinner jacket, and bride Sheldon Juanita DeLaney Lewis wearing lace gown, mantilla and eyeglasses, seated in back of Impala convertible
